<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>West Coast Homecare Services | Peace of Mind</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Comfortaa:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">

    <style>
        /* BRAND COLORS IDENTIFIED */
        :root {
            --brand-pink: #E6007E;   /* From your logo's heart/text */
            --brand-blue: #32B5E5;   /* From your logo's heart/text */
            --brand-navy: #1A2B49;   /* Professional dark navy for text */
            --sand: #F4F1EA;         /* Soft background neutral */
            --white: #ffffff;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Comfortaa', cursive;
            margin: 0;
            color: var(--brand-navy);
            background-color: var(--white);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* --- CENTERED NAVIGATION HEADER --- */
        header {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr 1.2fr; /* Centers the middle column */
            align-items: center;
            padding: 0 5%;
            background: var(--white);
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            height: 90px;
        }

        /* Left: Logo & Reg */
        .header-left {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
        }
        .logo-small { height: 55px; width: auto; border-radius: 50%; }
        .logo-details { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
        .logo-text { 
            font-weight: 700; 
            font-size: 0.85rem; 
            line-height: 1.1; 
            margin: 0;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .reg-no { font-size: 0.6rem; opacity: 0.7; margin-top: 2px; color: var(--brand-navy); }

        /* Center: Menu Items */
        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 30px;
            height: 100%;
        }
        nav a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--brand-navy);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            position: relative;
            height: 100%;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }
        /* Blue Underline Style */
        nav a:hover, nav a.active {
            color: var(--brand-blue);
        }
        nav a:hover::after, nav a.active::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 4px;
            background: var(--brand-blue);
        }

        /* Right: Social/Contact Icons */
        .header-right {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            gap: 22px;
        }
        .header-right a {
            color: var(--brand-navy);
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            transition: transform 0.2s, color 0.2s;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .header-right a:hover {
            color: var(--brand-pink); /* Pink pop on hover */
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        /* --- HERO SECTION --- */
        .hero {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 60px 8%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 70%, var(--sand) 100%);
        }
        .hero-text { flex: 1; max-width: 550px; }
        .hero-text h1 { font-size: 2.8rem; line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .hero-text h1 span { color: var(--brand-pink); }
        .hero-text p { font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 30px; color: var(--brand-navy); }

        .hero-art { flex: 1; display: flex; justify-content: center; }
        .hero-art img { width: 85%; max-width: 420px; border-radius: 50%; box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }

        /* --- SERVICE PILLS --- */
        .services { padding: 60px 8%; text-align: center; }
        .services h2 { color: var(--brand-navy); margin-bottom: 40px; }
        .service-grid {
            display: flex;
            gap: 12px;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .pill {
            background: var(--sand);
            color: var(--brand-navy);
            padding: 12px 28px;
            border-radius: 100px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .pill:hover { 
            background: var(--white); 
            border-color: var(--brand-blue); 
            color: var(--brand-blue);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(50, 181, 229, 0.1);
        }

        /* --- CONTACT & FOOTER --- */
        .contact-cta {
            background-color: var(--brand-blue);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 60px 8%;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .eval-btn {
            background-color: var(--brand-pink);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 18px 40px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .eval-btn:hover {
            background-color: var(--brand-navy);
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        footer {
            background: var(--brand-navy);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 40px 8%;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }
        .footer-logo { font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 10px; display: block; }
        .footer-reg { opacity: 0.5; font-size: 0.7rem; }

        @media (max-width: 950px) {
            header { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; height: auto; padding: 15px 5%; }
            nav { display: none; } /* Mobile menu usually requires a toggle */
            .hero { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
            .hero-text { margin-bottom: 40px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <div class="header-left">
            <img src="West CoastArtisticBanner.jpg" alt="West Coast Logo" class="logo-small">
            <div class="logo-details">
                <p class="logo-text">WEST COAST<br>HOMECARE</p>
                <span class="reg-no">REG: 2024/129640/07</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <nav>
            <a href="#" class="active">Home</a>
            <a href="#services">Services</a>
            <a href="#about">About</a>
            <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
        </nav>

        <div class="header-right">
            <a href="tel:0621247451" title="Call Nadine Saunders"><i class="fa-solid fa-phone"></i></a>
            <a href="mailto:info@westcoasthomecareservices.co.za" title="Email Us"><i class="fa-solid fa-envelope"></i></a>
            <a href="https://wa.me/27621247451" target="_blank" title="Chat on WhatsApp"><i class="fa-brands fa-whatsapp"></i></a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-text">
            <h1>Giving you <br><span>Peace of Mind.</span></h1>
            <p>Taking Home Based Services To The Next Level. Professional care for the elderly, frail, and those needing specialized dementia support.</p>
            <a href="tel:0621247451" class="eval-btn">FREE HOME EVALUATION</a>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-art">
            <img src="West CoastArtisticBanner.jpg" alt="Artistic Banner">
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="services" id="services">
        <h2>Our Home Care Services</h2>
        <div class="service-grid">
            <div class="pill">Day & Night Care</div>
            <div class="pill">Meal Preparation</div>
            <div class="pill">Light Housekeeping</div>
            <div class="pill">Medication Reminders</div>
            <div class="pill">Hygiene & Dressing</div>
            <div class="pill">Dementia Care</div>
            <div class="pill">24h Frail Care</div>
            <div class="pill">Personalised Proposals</div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="contact-cta" id="contact">
        <h2>Need help with a loved one?</h2>
        <p>Call Nadine Saunders today for a personalized evaluation of your home care needs.</p>
        <a href="tel:0621247451" class="eval-btn">CALL 062 124 7451</a>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <span class="footer-logo">WEST COAST HOMECARE SERVICES (Pty) Ltd</span>
        <p>Nadine Saunders | info@westcoasthomecareservices.co.za</p>
        <span class="footer-reg">REG: 2024/129640/07 | Giving you Peace of Mind</span>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
